-79/s75x75_c1/20254613a3d434a2f18f7f60ac45ec36d5d360da.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/b5470d37b5a94a6042f9e4afffe55bea/70d8a0074bcf5a51-79/s100x200/511643918cdd836725d94cf762240934b5deeffd.jpg 92w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/b5470d37b5a94a6042f9e4afffe55bea/70d8a0074bcf5a51-79/s250x400/dc7da4c89eb36686fd3de394b0f518db7e172324.jpg 185w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/b5470d37b5a94a6042f9e4afffe55bea/70d8a0074bcf5a51-79/s400x600/bf9b9f40f56ad860404fff1e6c3208e290e2ac85.jpg 277w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/b5470d37b5a94a6042f9e4afffe55bea/70d8a0074bcf5a51-79/s500x750/7873b54717598ccc28576f052d2845f552faa46f.jpg 346w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/b5470d37b5a94a6042f9e4afffe55bea/70d8a0074bcf5a51-79/s540x810/a7ad086ac87aedc7c698d0d92606460f668424d4.jpg 374w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/b5470d37b5a94a6042f9e4afffe55bea/70d8a0074bcf5a51-79/s640x960/98a8bf640bfb51b047e0f062969eafaf6a9299a9.jpg 443w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/b5470d37b5a94a6042f9e4afffe55bea/70d8a0074bcf5a51-79/s1280x1920/dc7a5e92b5b0bd73593f5f6cc07fced1500103f4.jpg 886w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/b5470d37b5a94a6042f9e4afffe55bea/70d8a0074bcf5a51-79/s2048x3072/44c7cd9c552bed7864898817af6d33660af4bbce.jpg 945w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 945px) 100vw, 945px\"/></figure></div></blockquote><p>sounds very similar to a radio story i heard in 2014 ago about credit card debt. the debt got sold to a collection company and a couple received a court summons. they knew they had taken on debt, but they were confused about who this new company was and where specifically the number they were supposed to owe came from. </p><p>they show up in court and just ask the lawyer for the collection company: can you prove where this number comes from? Do you have a contract showing that you purchased our debt? probably luckily for them, a reporter researching a book on the topic showed up and asked the same questions.</p><p>10 minutes later they get in front of the judge and the collection company drops the whole case and theyre free to go. story is below, it has a transcript in the link too</p><p class=\"npf_link\" data-npf='{\"type\":\"link\",\"url\":\"https://href.li/?https://www.thisamericanlife.org/532/magic-words/prologue-0\",\"display_url\":\"https://href.li/?https://www.thisamericanlife.org/532/magic-words/prologue-0\",\"title\":\"Prologue - This American Life\",\"description\":\"Ira talks to reporter Jake Halpern about a scene he saw take place in a Georgia courtroom where a couple uttered some magic words that seeme\",\"site_name\":\"This American Life\",\"poster\":[{\"media_key\":\"5171fe97d0ac0678dd1be4e37807d66a:0f44e02e2c373236-7b\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\",\"width\":1142,\"height\":600}]}'><a href=\"https://href.li/?https://www.thisamericanlife.org/532/magic-words/prologue-0\" target=\"_blank\">Prologue - This American Life</a></p></blockquote><div class=\"npf_row\"><div><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"2046\" data-orig-width=\"1096\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/18a83e9c5dda61b26b80a24385a73fab/4d4c5a923d0d4f81-a1/s640x960/8b670559dd15479e5d5b6e56009769e8109fb301.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"2046\" data-orig-width=\"1096\" alt=\"Re-upping this for no particular reason. The easiest lawsuit I ever filed and any one can do it. \n\nIn my experience, none of these student loan servicers / loan sharks kept proper chain of title. You challenge their ownership, they decline to respond, you get a default judgment. https://t.co/U5is6QYbvv\n\n— Brian Manookian (@BrianManookian) July 1, 2023\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/18a83e9c5dda61b26b80a24385a73fab/4d4c5a923d0d4f81-a1/s75x75_c1/bea60988e6f0ac4c029bb54ce973c2fe05b48c43.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/18a83e9c5dda61b26b80a24385a73fab/4d4c5a923d0d4f81-a1/s100x200/8a69e8586561b0842c0f17579edb7fdfd895eb29.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/18a83e9c5dda61b26b80a24385a73fab/4d4c5a923d0d4f81-a1/s250x400/63b93ae06f78417195a34465a383e3f7496dc3d1.jpg 214w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/18a83e9c5dda61b26b80a24